        <Parent_String>French-door locks [300033421], door locks [300033419], locks by location or context [300048657], locks (securing devices) [300033407], securing devices [300080839], securing devices and securing device components [300246367], finish hardware (hardware) [300045309], hardware by form [300145797], hardware (components) [300033260], components by general context [300241581], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
